docs.abstract: WikiLeaks makes public latest batch of emails hacked from account of John D Podesta while he was senior adviser to Hillary Clinton in 2015;  material sheds light on damage control undertaken by Clinton staff in effort to protect Pres Obama from growing perception that he knew about Clinton's use of private email server during her tenure at State Dept.
